   912	new mode is inserted into the gap thus created. If there are many field
   913	modes, the result is a slight increase $\rho_1(\nu)$ in mode density in
   914	the vicinity of $\Omega$. To calculate it, note that if the field mode
   915	$\omega_i$ is shifted a very small amount to
